[SIZE=5][B]Flyiron's Drugs Plugin (DrugsV2)[/B][/SIZE]
[B][URL='https://github.com/EthanManners/Flyirons-Drugs-Plugin']GitHub / Full Technical Documentation[/URL][/B]

[URL='https://discord.gg/SaxTyAFHV9'][B]Discord[/B][/URL]

Flyiron's Drugs is a [B]risk vs reward survival gameplay plugin[/B] for SMP and PvP servers.
Players can use powerful items for short-term buffs, but overuse can lead to [B]tolerance, addiction, withdrawal, and overdose[/B].

This is not a "one-time gimmick" plugin. It's built for long-running worlds with economies, conflict, and supply chains.

[SIZE=5][B]What Your Players Get[/B][/SIZE]
[LIST]
[*]Unique consumables with strong upsides and real downsides
[*]Persistent tolerance (effects get weaker if spammed)
[*]Addiction and withdrawal systems that matter over time
[*]Overdose danger for high-risk playstyles
[*]Cannabis strain progression + mutation system
[*]Bongs and carts with durability-based usage
[*]Achievement progression and unlocks
[/LIST]

[SIZE=5][B]Core Commands[/B][/SIZE]
[SIZE=4][B]Player Commands[/B][/SIZE]
[LIST]
[*][B]/drugs[/B] - Open the main menu
[*][B]/drugs help[/B] - View command help
[*][B]/tolerance[/B] - Check your tolerance/potency levels
[*][B]/strains[/B] - Open the cannabis strains menu
[*][B]/drugs achievements[/B] - Open achievements menu
[/LIST]

[SIZE=4][B]Admin Commands[/B][/SIZE]
[LIST]
[*][B]/drugs give <player> <drugId|cureId|bong|all> [amount][/B] - Give items for events/testing/staff actions
[*][B]/drugs purge <player>[/B] - Reset a player's tolerance + overdose counters
[*][B]/drugs reload[/B] - Reload plugin configs
[*][B]/drugs list[/B] - List all loaded drugs
[*][B]/drugs overdose reload[/B] - Reload overdose settings only
[*][B]/drugs overdose reset <player>[/B] - Reset overdose attempts for one player
[*][B]/drugs achievements toggle[/B] - Shows achievement on/off guidance (set in config + reload)
[/LIST]

[SIZE=5][B]Drug Types Included[/B][/SIZE]
[LIST]
[*]High-risk combat drugs (Heroin, Fent, Glue)
[*]Stimulant/combat/mobility drugs (Cocaine, Meth, Molly)
[*]Cannabis forms (Blunt, Joint, Edible, Cart)
[*]Utility/fun option (Shrooms)
[/LIST]

[SIZE=5][B]Recovery & Consequences[/B][/SIZE]
[LIST]
[*]Cures like [B]Suboxone[/B] and [B]CBD[/B]
[*]Sleep-based recovery options (for configured drugs)
[*]Enchanted Golden Apple full reset route
[*]Withdrawal and overdose behavior configurable per server
[/LIST]

[SIZE=5][B]Server Owner Notes[/B][/SIZE]
[LIST]
[*]Works out of the box with included default configs
[*]Fully config-driven if you want to rebalance
[*]Supports PlaceholderAPI for scoreboard/HUD integrations
[*]Recommended texture pack included in the repository
[/LIST]

